SIMPLE: rosedrop
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rosedrop
<hw>Rose"drop`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A lozenge having a
rose flavor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A kind of earring.</def>
<rj><au>Simmonds.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A ruddy eruption upon the nose
caused by drinking ardent spirits; a grog blossom.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rosefinch</ent>⟦br⟧
